monday night that a majority of 24 justices on the court supported 
the decrees 
the deadline for the court to rule was today but normally 
several days pass before court rulings are made public 
seven bombs exploded in colombian cities monday night two in 
the carribbean coast city of barranquilla three in the port city 
of santa marta and two in the capital of bogota national police 
said 
