used to determine taxation is mostly lowincome housing or 
military installations though the federal government pays the 
district about 200000 a year the bases cannot be taxed 
the lack of money means edgewood spends about 3600 per pupil 
per year other texas school districts spend anywhere from 2100 
to 19300 per pupil depending on the districts tax base 
